  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Robot Arena Survivors</strong> is a single-player arena auto-shooter where you're fighting against waves of hostile robots using a powerful arsenal made of hover tank units. Customize your own set of abilities and dismantle your enemies to claim your fame into the leaderboards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841950/extras/2fc6ddbea4ab7c2c916f3d37afb4ad49.poster.avif?t=1747120481\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841950/extras/2fc6ddbea4ab7c2c916f3d37afb4ad49.webm?t=1747120481\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841950/extras/2fc6ddbea4ab7c2c916f3d37afb4ad49.mp4?t=1747120481\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841950/extras/de606fd7137f5c7a02b72a9c93b50199.avif?t=1747120481\" width=616 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use any of the different available hover tank units to get the job done. They all have their own characteristics and weaponry!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841950/extras/366070a2fcad43ff5d48d2366193098d.poster.avif?t=1747120481\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841950/extras/366070a2fcad43ff5d48d2366193098d.webm?t=1747120481\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841950/extras/366070a2fcad43ff5d48d2366193098d.mp4?t=1747120481\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841950/extras/6a4a4dba3c37d20a38aafa68ec88ae97.avif?t=1747120481\" width=616 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your own ability deck by choosing from various abilities to unlock, fine-tuning your gameplay experience and creating your own loadouts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841950/extras/7aa5aa9540331c2fb11040ae8ba52896.poster.avif?t=1747120481\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841950/extras/7aa5aa9540331c2fb11040ae8ba52896.webm?t=1747120481\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841950/extras/7aa5aa9540331c2fb11040ae8ba52896.mp4?t=1747120481\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841950/extras/d54d3bedce0ebfab0f973553a1444379.avif?t=1747120481\" width=616 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather the materials dropped by defeated enemies to level-up and unlock powerful rewards while fighting off the swarms of robots!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841950/extras/d375c23fec51e8ef2fb1e02533882a11.poster.avif?t=1747120481\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841950/extras/d375c23fec51e8ef2fb1e02533882a11.webm?t=1747120481\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841950/extras/d375c23fec51e8ef2fb1e02533882a11.mp4?t=1747120481\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841950/extras/e768e9a5359df72224cf0df2cb492cfa.avif?t=1747120481\" width=616 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight against hostile robots from various locations, in different game modes, and challenge yourself to reach the top 20 of the best pilots!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841950/extras/2995a35dfb1bc8376e484264ffd3e17b.poster.avif?t=1747120481\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841950/extras/2995a35dfb1bc8376e484264ffd3e17b.webm?t=1747120481\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841950/extras/2995a35dfb1bc8376e484264ffd3e17b.mp4?t=1747120481\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841950/extras/2ed8b2e08cedcd693f3dde2dce38ac05.avif?t=1747120481\" width=616 height=64 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A set of <strong>5 arenas to discover</strong> with their own design, hazards and robotic enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The choice between <strong>3 different challenges per arena</strong>: a <strong>standard mode</strong> without ranking, and <strong>two ranked modes</strong>: Endless and Protect the Core, with their own <strong>dedicated online leaderboards</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A selection of <strong>8 unique hover tank units</strong> with their own advantages and weaponry.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More than <strong>20 different abilities</strong> to choose from in order to <strong>customize and build your own ability decks</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A total of <strong>13 base stats to permanently upgrade</strong> by progressing through the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tens of Steam Achievements</strong> to unlock!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841950/extras/9cf80165902a062673d0b732dbe5427c.avif?t=1747120481\" width=616 height=64 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A dual-stick shooter </strong>: respecting the traditional bullet-heaven (or reverse bullet-hell) genre, the game doesn't feature any manual aiming or weapon activation.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A scenario/campaign based game</strong> : the game is meant to be enjoyed for short or long sessions of gameplay where you can freely disconnect your brain and dismantle hundreds of robots with your tanks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A multiplayer game </strong>: the only way for you to compare your performance with others is by using the various available online leaderboards associated to the game modes and arenas. The game will not receive any multiplayer capabilities. </p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Robot Arena Survivors</strong> is a single-player arena auto-shooter where you're fighting against waves of hostile robots using a powerful arsenal made of hover tank units. Customize your own set of abilities and dismantle your enemies to claim your fame into the leaderboards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841950/extras/2fc6ddbea4ab7c2c916f3d37afb4ad49.poster.avif?t=1747120481\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841950/extras/2fc6ddbea4ab7c2c916f3d37afb4ad49.webm?t=1747120481\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841950/extras/2fc6ddbea4ab7c2c916f3d37afb4ad49.mp4?t=1747120481\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841950/extras/de606fd7137f5c7a02b72a9c93b50199.avif?t=1747120481\" width=616 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use any of the different available hover tank units to get the job done. They all have their own characteristics and weaponry!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841950/extras/366070a2fcad43ff5d48d2366193098d.poster.avif?t=1747120481\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2841950/extras/366070a2fcad43ff5d48d2366193098d.webm?t=1747120481\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/app